{"tid":7652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"26歲人，過左26個單身聖誕","createTime":"2016-11-28T02:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T00:34:51.000Z","uid":31946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8fc94a2484cf8bee512ed30e9e357535f78017f","tid":7652,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"曾經有拍過拖 不過拍得唔耐<br />\n3-6個月左右就散，老實講句唔識兩個人相處之道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n單身返幾年 識女仔又唔識 同女仔傾下計都唔敢<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b36ec1469eb3f2edb19723afe3b25aab3786f6","tid":7652,"uid":31137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"相處之道都唔識，唔好話識女仔，點係社會生存都成問題⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c06f6738d1cf6a4581dec8894b96cbb523ebf6f","tid":7652,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:44:21.000Z","msg":"不要再說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f73206146a0a32baad965646e2bb99a95cc514","tid":7652,"uid":9252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:44:24.000Z","msg":"唔緊要，陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f512054798ac8973cc437b586ef69c941f31a8d","tid":7652,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相處之道都唔識，唔好話識女仔，點係社會生存都成問題⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 兩個人既相處之道<br />\n唔係人與人之間果d<br />\n同班手足不知幾fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106b59dda756f8f64d8782cf78aeddd4f7ee9f5b","tid":7652,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"事關我發現最近同d識左無耐